Sally Mortemore https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sally_Mortemore 0 Sally Mortemore is an English stage, film and television actress. She appeared in Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets, where she played Madame Pince, the librarian of Hogwarts. Sally_Mortemore is an_English_stage , film_and_television_actress . She appeared in Harry_Potter and the_Chamber of Secrets , where she played Madame_Pince , the_librarian of Hogwarts .
